28:29.526 --> 28:33.111
If you don't know this about me for a long time in my life, I had a really bad stutter.

28:33.191 --> 28:34.472
Moses is my boy, I get it.

28:35.093 --> 28:39.238
It is overwhelming when you're going, I feel a certain way, but I don't have the words yet.

