He didn't say disappointment.

29:16.037 --> 29:17.298
He didn't say wash out.

29:19.074 --> 29:24.182
He said, Moses, for you, he's saying, son, daughter.

29:26.766 --> 29:30.873
If God can call Moses by his name and median, he can call you by your name today.

29:32.255 --> 29:44.294
So as we worship, whatever it looks like for you to come back to God, if you've been running, if you're feeling numb, if you're feeling angry, if you've been tired, don't climb up to God today.

29:45.055 --> 29:46.898
Remember, that's how every other faith works.

29:47.938 --> 29:50.922
If you try to climb up somewhere, you're gonna realize God was waiting for you where you left.

29:51.643 --> 29:55.589
He's here right now with you today.

29:57.551 --> 30:14.495
Wherever that finds you, whatever you feel culture pressing in and asking you to achieve or perform to gain the status of, God is the only entity, the only being in the universe, the great I am, Yahweh, where you have nothing to prove.

30:15.476 --> 30:16.818
You have no one to impress.

30:17.666 --> 30:23.915
His love for you is unshakeable, unquantifiable, incomprehensible, and infinite.

